magic_df = cb.MagicDataFrame(os.path.join(PROJECT_WD, 'sites.txt'), dmodel=
    DMODEL)
directions = magic_df.df.loc['1', 'bed_dip_direction']
self.assertEqual(sorted(directions, key=lambda x, y=0: int(x - y) if (
    isinstance(x, float) or isinstance(x, int)) and (isinstance(y, float) or
    isinstance(y, int)) else -1), [None, 135, 135])
magic_df.front_and_backfill(cols=['bed_dip_direction'])
directions = magic_df.df.loc['1', 'bed_dip_direction']
self.assertEqual(sorted(directions), [135, 135, 135])
